      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Gabor Szots</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:194px;\"><a href=\"/File:GaborSzots.JPG\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/f/f6/GaborSzots.JPG\" width=\"192\" height=\"280\" class=\"thumbimage\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:GaborSzots.JPG\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Gábor at <a href=\"/MASPV_2004\" title=\"MASPV 2004\">MASPV 2004</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Gábor Szõts</b>,<br />\na Hungarian chess player <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>, and as tester of chess programs, member of the <a href=\"/CCRL\" title=\"CCRL\">CCRL</a> group. \nHe helped with the Hungarian translation for <a href=\"/Arena\" title=\"Arena\">Arena</a> and also served as <a href=\"/Category:Tournament_Director\" title=\"Category:Tournament Director\">tournament organizer</a> at various <a href=\"/Hungarian_Chessprogram_Open\" title=\"Hungarian Chessprogram Open\">Hungarian Chessprogram Open</a>. \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#2000_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2000 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#2005_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2005 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#2010_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2010 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#2015_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2015 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#2020_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2020 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Gabor_Szots&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2000_...\">2000 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Gabor_Szots&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: 2000 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=18&amp;t=34671&amp;p=131024\">Pepito 1.40 MMX LCT2 test</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Gabor Szots</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, October 02, 2001&#160;» <a href=\"/LCT_II\" title=\"LCT II\">LCT II</a>, <a href=\"/Pepito\" title=\"Pepito\">Pepito</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?t=41222&amp;p=156934\">Chezzz and EGTB's</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Gábor Szõts</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, February 12, 2003&#160;» <a href=\"/Chezzz\" title=\"Chezzz\">Chezzz</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=18&amp;t=47721\">New Hungarian Chess Program Champion!</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Gábor Szõts</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, May 31, 2004&#160;» <a href=\"/MASPV_2004\" title=\"MASPV 2004\">MASPV 2004</a>, <a href=\"/Merlin_(HU)\" title=\"Merlin (HU)\">Merlin</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2005_...\">2005 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Gabor_Szots&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: 2005 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=414513\">Spike</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Gabor Szots</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 27, 2005&#160;» <a href=\"/Spike\" title=\"Spike\">Spike</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=431904\">Has Thomas Gaksch become co-author of Fruit?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Gabor Szots</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 18, 2005&#160;» <a href=\"/Thomas_Gaksch\" title=\"Thomas Gaksch\">Thomas Gaksch</a>, <a href=\"/Fruit\" title=\"Fruit\">Fruit</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=490881\">Delfi as UCI</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Gabor Szots</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 02, 2006&#160;» <a href=\"/Delfi\" title=\"Delfi\">Delfi</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=50055\">Jim, do you remember?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Gábor Szots</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, March 26, 2009</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=31132\">Little Thought 1.04 64-bit 2-CPU</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Gabor Szots</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 18, 2009&#160;» <a href=\"/LittleThought\" title=\"LittleThought\">LittleThought</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2010_...\">2010 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Gabor_Szots&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: 2010 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=33259\">Deep Sjeng 50-move rule bug</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Gabor Szots</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 14, 2010&#160;» <a href=\"/Deep_Sjeng\" title=\"Deep Sjeng\">Deep Sjeng</a>, <a href=\"/Fifty-move_Rule\" title=\"Fifty-move Rule\">Fifty-move Rule</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=35554\">As though they were pondering</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Gabor Szots</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>,  July 23, 2010&#160;» <a href=\"/Pondering\" title=\"Pondering\">Pondering</a>, <a href=\"/Time_Management\" title=\"Time Management\">Time Management</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=43021\">Redqueen 1.1.1 64-bit - Is this a bug?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Gabor Szots</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 26, 2012&#160;» <a href=\"/RedQueen\" title=\"RedQueen\">RedQueen</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=51279\">32-bit and 64-bit java engines</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Gabor Szots</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 14, 2014&#160;» <a href=\"/Java\" title=\"Java\">Java</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=52522\">Question about syzygy bases</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Gabor Szots</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 02, 2014&#160;» <a href=\"/Syzygy_Bases\" title=\"Syzygy Bases\">Syzygy Bases</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=53902\">Similarity tests</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Gabor Szots</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 01, 2014</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2015_...\">2015 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Gabor_Szots&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: 2015 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=62290\">Strange beaviour of WyldChess under WinBoard</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Gabor Szots</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 27, 2016&#160;» <a href=\"/WyldChess\" title=\"WyldChess\">WyldChess</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=68095\">Off topic - Who is authorized?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Gabor Szots</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 28, 2018</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=69024\">Java problem</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Gabor Szots</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 24, 2018&#160;» <a href=\"/Java\" title=\"Java\">Java</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=69057\">Frank Walter</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Gabor Szots</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 26, 2018&#160;» <a href=\"/FrankWalter\" title=\"FrankWalter\">FrankWalter</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=71355\">Move overhead</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Gabor Szots</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 25, 2019</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2020_...\">2020 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Gabor_Szots&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: 2020 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=76552\">How much work is it to train an NNUE?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Gabor Szots</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 11, 2021&#160;» <a href=\"/NNUE\" title=\"NNUE\">NNUE</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Gabor_Szots&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://ratings.fide.com/profile/711667\">Szots, Gabor FIDE Chess Profile</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Gabor_Szots&amp;action=edit&amp;section=8\" title=\"Edit section: Refere